==German==
===Etymology===
From Germanic ''*faita-'' "fat".
===Adjective===
'''fett'''
# [[fat]]
#:''Der Typ ist echt '''fett'''.'' - This guy is really adipose.
# [[phat]]
#:''Der Typ ist echt '''fett'''.'' - This guy is really cool.
# [[profitable]]
#:''Sie hat nen [[fetten]] Vertrag an Land gezogen'' - She achieved a very profitable treaty.

